        "id": 1003190
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-03-18T22:12:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think I don\u0027t understand what you mean by (1), could you clarify?\n\nAlso, IMO (2) is a reason why it *could* be a string, but the real reason why we were considering string was because we think maybe sometime later modes will be specified by some tuple of options (e.g. (submit on success, use rts)), and name will be arbitrary and may be project-specific. (Is that what you were thinking Andrii?)\n\nI\u0027m still not fully convinced it should be a string rather than enum myself.",
      "parentUuid": "33086e31_a37cbcb1",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 52,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 52,
        "endChar": 22
      },
      "revId": "252b4147c2efd0884d0a160b29745a812d0dc5c1",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "a5642369_4ca4093d",
        "filename": "cv/api/recipe/v1/cq.proto",
        "patchSetId": 1
      },
      "lineNbr": 52,
