      "writtenOn": "2021-03-19T00:37:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e I think I don\u0027t understand what you mean by (1), could you clarify?\n\nCV defines run mode as string. If we make it a enum here, it means we need to add a conversion logic in CV to convert the mode string to an enum. I don\u0027t think it will scale well because everytime a new run mode is introduced, we must update this proto and corresponding conversion logic.",
      "parentUuid": "3dd6f8fd_7529a913",
